I HAVE NEVER ever been rejected so many times in the past few years as in all my life... Getting what I wanted never was this difficult.. so I must have changed my methods somehow and people are like no, no dice. Um, as for broke people, we all get paid today so we will probably be spending our money foolishly on fast food and shit watch out. today and thursday SSI checks in the bank so I'm thinking either a trip to IL today or tomorrow for cigs, Ive been so broke I bought tops and hav been rolling my own i just sneezed, and some lung butter came up and it was salty gross well not really its a natural bodily function, sneezing, dunno what it means but yea that just happened that was like 2 days ago, i brushed like 4 times that day as opposed to just once yesterday in the morning and once or twice this morning already so I have to remember to do it at least one more time before bed I am so miserable here, its cold, im out of smokes, i have no good food... i cant sleep very well because I have no bed and The couch isnt endlessly comfortable so i wake up and switch sides, broken half not broken half floor broken half floor not broken half wake up eat try to go back to sleep its an endless cycle, it really sucks I really wish I hadnt moved out of my moms house I have no car. I have no job. With my check I Was gunna pay my rent, my internet bill, and then possibly look into signing up for some classes at MATC to keeep me busy.. I Really dont know what to do and going back to school is starting to sound fun. also i have to commit to buying that stupid couch and my cigs.. so its gunna be tough. me this morning after i drew on triangle eyebrows and a beard. IDK why but i like it.
